this is how you do it guys.
download and install, activate with the key, update the software then add TU into hosts file right away so it cant ping their database.
Rightclick on Notepad then run as admin, click file, click open, type hosts into file name, click open.

Just add "127.0.0.1 secure.tuneup.com" without quotes into the hosts file list, save and you are done.

It is the full version and will not update anymore after this but it works so well for me.
